title: 1BR+Den in North Loop - Beautiful Downtown Views!
posting_body: ['Borealis is a walkable, bikeable retreat in the vibrant North Loop neighborhood.', 'Featuring modern, upgraded interiors, beautiful (and functional!)', 'floor plans, and superior customer service, Borealis has received rave reviews from happy residents since opening its doors in March 2018.', 'Visit our Google page or read more about the building here: <URL>', '#404 -- Plan N', 'Plan N is a one bedroom plus den, one bath layout available on the 4th floor.', 'This unit features a balcony and downtown views, as well as abundant storage space.', 'Finishes include warm maple plank flooring, a large black granite island countertop and white shaker cabinetry!', 'Natural light pours through the floor to ceiling windows!', 'For info on amenities and to apply: <URL>', 'For your Instagram fix: @borealisnorthloop', 'Prices subject to change.', 'Minneapolis -- Mpls -- North Loop -- Warehouse District -- NE -- Northeast -- U of M -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Scandinavian -- Mid-Century Modern -- Bike Friendly -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging -- New Construction']
